OL,3,CThe secret footage from Warwickshire
OL,4,Cabattoir under police investigation
OL,6,FMore than 100 people had gathered
OL,7,Foutside T&S Abattoir in Arley by the
OL,8,Ftime my camera operator and I arrived
OL,9,Fon Wednesday.
OL,11,FIt was the third demonstration in less
OL,12,Fthan a week and the road was lined
OL,13,Fwith angry protestors, many of whom
OL,14,Fwere holding banners.
OL,16,FThe gates of the slaughterhouse were
OL,17,Fshut but it was clear from the
OL,18,Fmovement of staff that work was still
OL,19,Ftaking place.
