OL,3,CThe secret footage from Warwickshire
OL,4,Cabattoir under police investigation
OL,6,FAround that time, residents say they
OL,7,Fbegan to suspect potential
OL,8,Fmistreatment of animals.
OL,10,FCarolyn said: "We realised that the
OL,11,Fnoises the animals were making were
OL,12,Fnot of animals that were being looked
OL,13,Fafter properly.
OL,15,F"There was such fear and panic in the
OL,16,Fnoise that was emanating in the
OL,17,Fvillage. And we were really fearful
OL,18,Ffor the welfare of the animals in
OL,19,Fthere."
