OL,4,Cabattoir under police investigation
OL,6,FDuring our filming, a round of
OL,7,Fapplause broke out among the
OL,8,Fprotestors.
OL,10,FThey were celebrating the arrival of
OL,11,FJoey Carbstrong, the Australian film-
OL,12,Fmaker and animal rights activist,
OL,13,Fwhose hidden camera video of T&S
OL,14,FAbattoir had been made public the
OL,15,Fprevious week.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/14
