OL,3,CThe secret footage from Warwickshire
OL,4,Cabattoir under police investigation
OL,6,FDuring the filming, Joey claimed to
OL,7,Fhave uncovered multiple instances of
OL,8,Fpossible illegality at the now Halal
OL,9,Fslaughterhouse, including the rough
OL,10,Ftreatment of sheep and goats, as well
OL,11,Fas ineffective restraining equipment.
OL,13,FSome animals also appeared to have
OL,14,Fbeen dismembered whilst still showing
OL,15,Fsigns of life.
OL,17,FThe video, uploaded to YouTube, had
OL,18,Falready been watched by more than
OL,19,F100,000 people, including Carolyn -
OL,20,Fwho said it was so "distressing".
