OL,6,FShe told ITV News Central: "I just
OL,7,Fcried and cried. I was crying for
OL,8,Fabout four hours.
OL,10,F"It was so distressing, I was
OL,11,Fdevastated. Someone tried to call me
OL,12,Fand I told them I'd have to call them
OL,13,Fback because I was so distraught."
OL,15,FNow something of a celebrity in Arley,
OL,16,FJoey took time shaking hands with
OL,17,Fmembers of the crowd before coming
OL,18,Fover for our interview.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/14
