OL,6,FAn ardent vegan, he told me that in an
OL,7,Fideal world, he would like to see all
OL,8,Fslaughterhouses closed down but now
OL,9,Fsaw it as his life's mission to
OL,10,Funcover potential breaches of animal
OL,11,Fwelfare in the meat industry.
OL,13,FI began by asking what his reaction
OL,14,Fwas when he heard about the concerns
OL,15,Fof residents in Arley.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/14
