OL,3,CThe secret footage from Warwickshire
OL,4,Cabattoir under police investigation
OL,6,FHe said: "I came straight down here
OL,7,Fand we had a look and just sussed the
OL,8,Fplace out a bit and I'm mostly
OL,9,Fconcerned with what's going on to the
OL,10,Fanimals so then we took the tip off
OL,11,Fseriously and initiated the
OL,12,Finvestigation."
OL,14,FBy installing secret cameras, Joey
OL,15,Fsaid he recorded more than 200 hours
OL,16,Fof footage inside T&S Abattoir in July
OL,17,F2024.
