OL,3,CThe secret footage from Warwickshire
OL,4,Cabattoir under police investigation
OL,6,FAmong the possible breaches of animal
OL,7,Fwelfare exposed during his video, were
OL,8,Fanimals appearing to have limbs
OL,9,Fremoved whilst still showing signs of
OL,10,Flife.
OL,12,FUnder government regulations, Halal
OL,13,Fslaughterers must wait a minimum of 20
OL,14,Fseconds after cutting the throats of
OL,15,Fsheep and goats to ensure they have
OL,16,Flost consciousness before the animals
OL,17,Fare moved.
