OL,6,FOn Thursday, Warwickshire Police
OL,7,Fannounced that "in light of the video"
OL,8,Fit had recorded "a suspected offence
OL,9,Fof unnecessary suffering to a
OL,10,Fprotected animal under animal welfare
OL,11,Flegislation."
OL,13,FThe Food Standards Agency meanwhile,
OL,14,Ftold us that it was taking the footage
OL,15,Fseriously and had taken action to
OL,16,Fsuspend several individuals from
OL,17,Fhandling live animals.
