OL,6,FIn a statement it said: "We had
OL,7,Falready identified and appropriately
OL,8,Fenforced animal welfare failures at
OL,9,Fthis establishment prior to being sent
OL,10,Fthe covert footage.
OL,12,F"Since last summer, we've put in place
OL,13,Fincreased Official presence and have
OL,14,Fcontinued to work onsite to ensure
OL,15,Fimprovements were made.
