OL,6,F"It would be inappropriate to comment
OL,7,Ffurther at this stage as the
OL,8,Finvestigation is ongoing but we will
OL,9,Fnot hesitate to take more action where
OL,10,Frequired as we have a zero-tolerance
OL,11,Fapproach to animal welfare breaches."
OL,13,FAs for the T&S Abattoir, it said it
OL,14,Fwill cooperate with any investigation
OL,15,Fand said in a statement: "We have
OL,16,Ftaken the necessary action and
OL,17,Fterminated contracts of those thought
OL,18,Fto be involved as this goes completely
OL,19,Fagainst our values and animal welfare
OL,20,Fpolicies.
