OL,6,FIt goes onto say: "The footage is
OL,7,Fthought to have been taken in July
OL,8,F2024 and continual improvements have
OL,9,Fbeen made since that time, including
OL,10,Fadding more CCTV, improvement of
OL,11,Frestraining equipment and
OL,12,Fincorporating a 20+ second timer.
OL,14,FThey also say they've introduced more
OL,15,Fexperienced management to oversee
OL,16,Foperations to ensure that our animal
OL,17,Fwelfare policy is always adhered to."
