OL,6,FDuring our filming residents told me
OL,7,Ftheir campaign against T&S Abattoir
OL,8,Fwas nothing to do with the fact it was
OL,9,Fnow a Halal slaughterhouse.
OL,11,FThey, as well as Joey, said their
OL,12,Fprotests were purely about minimising
OL,13,Fthe suffering of animals in their
OL,14,Ffinal moments.
